00:00:42.356 --> 00:00:48.049
" I just want to give all the glory, honor, and praise to the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:00:48.049 --> 00:00:54.051
He is the Healer, healing the sick the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:00:54.051 --> 00:00:57.020
He is a good God and a Healer.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:01:04.720
